(I GTG.  Cya all tomorrow.)

::DarkMouse::

She finally stopped shaking and walked after Tarantulas.   She still 
felt the creepiness of the place.  Something about the caves felt 
unnatural and forboading.  She looked and saw the bodies of the long 
dead aliens on the floor.  She felt her stomach turn upside down. 

She stopped and leaned against a wall to catch her breath.  She 
transformed into mouse mode and went on.  She sniffed the air and 
smelled something strange.  It smelt like a strange bot and something 
that reeked of decay and evil.  It made hr nose twitch and her spark 
pound.
